headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Nothing to Declare
content: The air freight business is full of opportunities. But as ever in Los Santos, you need to be proactive - and a brand new aircraft hangar is just the starting point you need. So, get yourself logged into the Free Trade Shipping Co app, acquire the cargo, make the sale. And if that sounds easy, remember every other dealer in the state has a vested interest in taking whatâ€™s yours, or at least seeing it crash and burn.
